        <div id="lB" class="tab-pane">
          <p>Follow the 4 simple steps below to play the quiz:
            1. Pick up the day’s ET, spot the quiz column and read the question. Click here (jpeg of column to pop-up) to see what the quiz column will look like.</br>
            2. The answer to the question will be in one of the articles in that day’s paper ONLY. Read the article to find the answer.</br>
            3. Send in your answer via SMS in the following format before 6:00 PM everyday:WINET<space>A/B/C/D to +91 9818505252
            4. Register yourself on Win With ET. Why Register?</br>
            a. Be eligible to win the Weekly and Grand prize. (You can continue to play without registering but you cannot win weekly/ Grand prize)</br>
            b. Keep track of your scores on a daily basis</br>
            c. See how your scores stack-up against other players</p>
        </div>
