          <p>How can you register?
            Played the Quiz-
            a. Log in with your mobile number and the password received via SMS
            b. If you cannot locate password, SMS WINET PWD to +91 9818505252
            c. Fill up the registration form
            Never played the Quiz
            a. Go to home page
            b. Click on New to Win With ET? Sign up
            c. Enter your mobile number
            d. Complete the Registration form and sign up
            e. You will receive a password via SMS
            f. Log in with your mobile number and the password received
            Please be sure to use the same mobile number to play the quiz every day. This number will act as your unique identity to which all points for correct answers get accumulated.</p>
